        "richtext_GBtyyM": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Effective Date: 13.08.2024</p><p>Welcome to Bravic! We are dedicated to revolutionizing the tech industry by merging cutting-edge performance with sophisticated design. At Bravic, we prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you interact with our website, products, and services.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_JHNHwz": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "1. Information We Collect",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_jC64Fj": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>a. Personal Information:</strong></p><p>We may collect personal information, including but not limited to names, contact details, and demographic information, when you voluntarily provide it to us through forms, surveys, or other interactions on our website.</p><p><strong>b. Non-Personal Information:</strong></p><p>We also collect non-personal information, such as browser type, device information, IP address, and other technical data that help us improve our website and services. This data is typically collected through cookies and other tracking technologies.</p><p><strong>c. Usage Data:</strong></p><p>We may collect information about your interactions with our website, including pages visited, links clicked, and time spent on various pages. This data helps us understand user behavior and enhance your experience on our platform.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_6WDYeH": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "2. How We Use Your Information",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_GNXaHW": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>a. To Provide and Improve Our Services:</strong></p><p>We use your personal information to process orders, deliver products, and provide customer support. We also use this data to enhance our website, products, and services, ensuring they meet your needs.</p><p><strong>b. To Communicate with You:</strong></p><p>We may use your contact information to send you updates about your order, promotional offers, newsletters, and other relevant information. You can opt out of receiving marketing communications at any time.</p><p><strong>c. To Enhance Security:</strong></p><p>Your data helps us monitor and improve the security of our website and services, protecting against unauthorized access, fraud, and other threats.</p><p><strong>d. To Personalize Your Experience:</strong></p><p>We may use the information we collect to personalize your experience on our website, tailoring content, recommendations, and advertisements to your interests.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_NDYVKa": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "3. Sharing Your Information",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_BXCgUk": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>a. With Third-Party Service Providers:</strong></p><p>We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website, processing payments, shipping products, and providing customer support. These partners are obligated to protect your information and use it solely for the purposes we specify.</p><p><strong>b. Legal Compliance:</strong></p><p>We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to valid legal requests by public authorities, including to meet national security or law enforcement requirements.</p><p><strong>c. Business Transfers:</strong></p><p>In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction. We will notify you via email or a prominent notice on our website of any such change in ownership or use of your personal information.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_rX8BkK": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "4. Your Rights and Choices",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_nReLqm": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p><strong>a. Access and Update Your Information:</strong></p><p>You have the right to access and update your personal information at any time by logging into your account or contacting our customer support team.</p><p><strong>b. Opt-Out of Marketing Communications:</strong></p><p>You can opt out of receiving promotional emails from Bravic by following the unsubscribe link in our emails or adjusting your preferences in your account settings.</p><p><strong>c. Request Deletion of Your Data:</strong></p><p>You may request that we delete your personal information by contacting us. Please note that we may retain certain information as required by law or for legitimate business purposes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_kGVBi8": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "5. Security Measures",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_4Mccjy": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. While we strive to safeguard your information, please understand that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_U3qKab": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_KamJ6e": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our website uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze site traffic, and personalize content. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings, but disabling cookies may affect the functionality of our website.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_VexCjU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "7. Third-Party Links",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_tPt9fN": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites or services that are not operated by Bravic. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties, and we encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_UWRqAL": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "8. Children's Privacy",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_YX8CCD": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Bravic does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If we become aware that we have inadvertently received such information, we will take steps to delete it as soon as possible.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_8ntR6E": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "9. Changes to This Privacy Policy",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_Ace3KH": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on our website and updating the effective date. Your continued use of our website and services after the changes are made constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_xp78Py": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "10. Contact Us",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
